		%p I design communications for both page and screen. I plan, create and build assets that enhance value for business and culture. In industry terms, I'm a senior designer and art director with over twelve years experience.

		%p I live in Melbourne, Australia with my wife and young daughter, where I also collect vinyl records of all kinds, read about software eating the world, and try to practise unwired boredom. Read more about my past work and what drives my sensibility:

